episodes.title: Dead Body in Bag Leads to Britain's Craziest Manhunt
episodes.description: England, 2023: Constance Marten was a British Aristocrat and ‘It Girl’. But the minute she left TB Joshua’s church, a place with cult-like and dark allegations against it, her life unravelled. And all of this would only be made worse when a man called Mark Gordon stepped into the picture, embarking on an obsessive love love that would soon lead them to a life on the run, with their newborn daughter strapped to Constance’s chest, in the freezing cold. episodes.description:
Here's a little snippet from a LIVE podcast recording I did with Killers, Cults and Queens (Cheryl and Nikki) at CrimeCon London! We discussed 3 different cults: Heaven's Gate, Love Has Won and last but not least... The Twin Flames Universe - run by Jeff and Shaleia. This snippet is just the Eleanor Neale section of the pod episode lol, but we're discussing the cult made famous by the Netflix Series Escaping Twin Flames... One of the darkest online cults of modern times.
